      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive refinement. This vehicle arrives in flawless, showroom condition, having been maintained to the most exacting standards. Every surface, from the deep-luster finish to the immaculate cabin, reflects a level of care that borders on the obsessive. For the collector or enthusiast who accepts only the finest, this remains a premier opportunity to acquire a vehicle of uncompromising quality and provenance.",
