      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a time capsule of pure automotive elegance. This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a symphony of chrome and hand-stitched leather that whispers stories of sunset drives along the coast. Its silhouette cuts through the air with the grace of a bygone era, gleaming under the streetlamps like a polished jewel. Every turn of the key is an invitation to escape the mundane, as the engine hums with a refined power that feels both nostalgic and vital. This masterpiece has been cherished, preserved not just as a vehicle, but as a testament to the art of the drive. Own a piece of history that doesn't just transport you\u2014it transforms you.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
